Flex has been telling his fans that he is broke and is trying to get back on track. He once posted that he won 250K and due to new money syndrome, he finished that within a month. Since then he taken time to get financial education so he can never make those mistakes again. The Vuzu Hustle winner bought himself a Nissan 1400 van for Seventy eight thousand. His fans feel he spent too much money for the model of the car. One of the people who also thought the money he spent was too was Sizwe Dlomo, but Flex is content with his decision. This is after he posted on Twitter that he is selling the car he won on the show. The van according to him will be more useful because he will use it for his delivery company called Thumela Express.   